  </order>
  <notepads>
    <notepad>
      <note>Integration test: live GET /repos/apache/hop/releases with LINK_HEADER pagination (per_page=5). No golden data — assertions only.

Passes when row_count >= ${PRM_MIN_RELEASE_ROWS} (default 6, so more than one page), row_count equals distinct tag_name, and tag_name/html_url look valid. Stays valid as new releases are published.
</note>
